00:48:15,559 --> 00:48:16,643
Not LY Distribution?

532
00:48:16,727 --> 00:48:19,896
Both you and Bon-geun
have some of LY Distribution's shares,

533
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:22,941
but Yoon-gyeom alone
owns the entirety of LY Pay.

534
00:48:24,443 --> 00:48:25,485
Wait, so…

535
00:48:26,194 --> 00:48:28,113
that one's listed
on the New York Stock Exchange?

536
00:48:28,196 --> 00:48:29,239
If he makes it work,

537
00:48:29,323 --> 00:48:32,159
it's only a matter of time
until he takes over the company.

538
00:48:59,686 --> 00:49:00,520
I'm sorry, sir.

539
00:49:01,813 --> 00:49:02,856
I cannot let you enter.

540
00:49:02,939 --> 00:49:05,025
How dare you treat me like this?

541
00:49:05,567 --> 00:49:06,985
Do you not know who I am?

542
00:49:07,069 --> 00:49:08,654
Chairman Kang has ordered

543
00:49:08,737 --> 00:49:11,365
not to let you into the building
until he gives permission.

544
00:49:11,448 --> 00:49:12,407
How dare you?

545
00:49:13,742 --> 00:49:15,452
-Call Yoon-gyeom.
-Yes, sir.

546
00:49:17,454 --> 00:49:19,706
You bunch won't get away with this!

547
00:49:20,207 --> 00:49:21,208
I'm sorry, sir.

548
00:49:24,419 --> 00:49:27,255
Yoon-gyeom, that punk.
How dare he screw me over like this?

549
00:49:28,256 --> 00:49:29,966
He screwed over his father too.

550
00:49:30,050 --> 00:49:31,510
He's really something else.

551
00:49:31,593 --> 00:49:33,512
Gosh, what a creepy little guy.

552
00:49:35,639 --> 00:49:36,473
What is it?

553
00:49:37,224 --> 00:49:38,141
I'm sorry, sir.

554
00:49:38,767 --> 00:49:41,436
You cannot enter
without Chairman Kang's permission.

555
00:49:41,520 --> 00:49:43,897
You son of a bitch!

556
00:49:49,444 --> 00:49:51,905
My son-in-law is a real son of a gun,

557
00:49:51,988 --> 00:49:53,448
but he's your actual son, isn't he?

558
00:49:54,241 --> 00:49:56,410
It looks like he backstabbed
his own father too.

559
00:49:57,244 --> 00:49:58,912
What a fine family.

560
00:49:58,995 --> 00:50:01,540
I mean, there's that video too.

561
00:50:01,623 --> 00:50:02,749
Maybe it runs in the family.

562
00:50:02,833 --> 00:50:04,501
Watch your mouth.

563
00:50:04,584 --> 00:50:06,586
This is happening all because of you.

564
00:50:06,670 --> 00:50:09,464
So you've decided to pin it all on me now?

565
00:50:09,548 --> 00:50:14,386
It all started because you were trying to
bite a chunk off of the company!

566
00:50:14,469 --> 00:50:17,431
LY has always been mine,
you fucking thieves!

567
00:50:17,514 --> 00:50:20,016
Don't you dare cuss at me,
you vulgar bastard!

568
00:50:20,100 --> 00:50:21,768
-You're a worthless parasite.
-What?

569
00:50:21,852 --> 00:50:24,354
A politician parasite
that feeds off of chaebols!

570
00:50:24,438 --> 00:50:25,814
-You…
-Hey!

571
00:50:28,608 --> 00:50:30,819
Watch what you're saying!

572
00:50:30,902 --> 00:50:32,821
You rude brat!

573
00:50:33,572 --> 00:50:34,614
Why you…

574
00:50:36,575 --> 00:50:37,492
Goddammit.

575
00:50:39,453 --> 00:50:40,704
Have you lost your mind?

576
00:50:40,787 --> 00:50:41,997
-Huh?
-You little brat!

577
00:50:43,665 --> 00:50:44,583
What the…

578
00:50:45,917 --> 00:50:47,878
-Sir.
-Let go!

579
00:50:47,961 --> 00:50:48,795
Stop, for goodness' sake!

580
00:50:48,879 --> 00:50:50,547
-Let go.
-What do you think you're doing?

581
00:50:50,630 --> 00:50:52,048
-Let go!
-Stop it.

582
00:50:52,132 --> 00:50:53,383
I said, stop it.

583
00:50:54,009 --> 00:50:55,927
You think you can stop me, you bastard?

584
00:50:56,011 --> 00:50:56,970
You asshole.

585
00:50:58,972 --> 00:51:00,056
How dare you hit him?

586
00:51:00,140 --> 00:51:03,602
LY is mine, you son of a bitch!

587
00:51:03,685 --> 00:51:05,729
You asshole, this is all your fault!

588
00:51:06,480 --> 00:51:09,232
You've lost it, haven't you?

589
00:51:09,316 --> 00:51:10,317
How dare you hit me?

590
00:51:11,526 --> 00:51:13,028
Who the hell was that?

591
00:51:13,111 --> 00:51:14,654
Come over here, you asshole!

592
00:51:16,198 --> 00:51:17,657
Are you all right, sir?

593
00:51:21,745 --> 00:51:23,830
-Gosh, that hurts!
-Oh, that hurts!

594
00:51:23,914 --> 00:51:25,040
You little shit.

595
00:51:47,687 --> 00:51:51,483
LY, THE WORLD'S LEADING COMPANY

596
00:52:00,158 --> 00:52:02,452
She must be truly oblivious.

597
00:52:03,453 --> 00:52:04,371
Okay.

598
00:52:09,668 --> 00:52:11,169
How dare she?

599
00:52:13,713 --> 00:52:14,631
Fine.

600
00:52:18,093 --> 00:52:20,136
LY Pay will be taking
a different approach…

601
00:52:20,220 --> 00:52:22,013
Chairman Kang is on TV, ma'am.

602
00:52:22,514 --> 00:52:25,809
…by introducing an unprecedented
biometric payment system

603
00:52:25,892 --> 00:52:29,479
that uses skin texture
and body temperature for transactions.

604
00:52:29,563 --> 00:52:31,314
LY Pay's historical…

605
00:52:31,398 --> 00:52:33,859
So LY is a global company now.

606
00:52:34,609 --> 00:52:36,278
Chairman Kang is amazing.

607
00:52:37,153 --> 00:52:38,864
Congratulations, Ms. Han.

608
00:52:38,947 --> 00:52:42,576
It looks like you and Chairman Kang
will be quite busy at the end of the year.

609
00:53:04,055 --> 00:53:05,515
I don't want to bother you,

610
00:53:06,683 --> 00:53:09,185
but I can't solve this issue
by myself this time.

611
00:53:10,854 --> 00:53:12,314
Please help me.

612
00:53:13,064 --> 00:53:15,275
Sure, just tell me what you need.

613
00:53:16,109 --> 00:53:18,612
The female bodyguard that Yoon-gyeom
assigned to me is in danger.

614
00:53:19,154 --> 00:53:20,822
She got caught by So-ra,

615
00:53:20,906 --> 00:53:24,075
but I can't rescue her alone
because So-ra probably has a lot of men.

616
00:53:24,159 --> 00:53:27,579
And I can't have anybody
finding out that you're helping me.

617
00:53:29,414 --> 00:53:31,333
What is that?

618
00:53:37,964 --> 00:53:39,174
Shit, it's the cops. Run!

619
00:53:48,600 --> 00:53:49,893
-Go after them.
-Yes, sir.

620
00:53:50,477 --> 00:53:52,479
Ms. Lee, are you okay?

621
00:53:52,562 --> 00:53:53,897
Wake up, Ms. Lee.

622
00:53:54,481 --> 00:53:55,315
Ms. Lee!

623
00:53:56,358 --> 00:53:58,151
Hurry and check where the ambulance is at.

624
00:53:58,234 --> 00:53:59,736
-Check on the ambulance.
-Ms. Lee!

625
00:54:02,864 --> 00:54:04,074
It'll arrive soon, sir.

626
00:54:04,574 --> 00:54:05,408
All right.

627
00:54:10,830 --> 00:54:12,165
Thanks, Myeong-hoon.

628
00:54:12,248 --> 00:54:13,083
I owe you one.

629
00:54:13,166 --> 00:54:14,501
Don't worry about it.

630
00:54:14,584 --> 00:54:16,294
If it weren't for you,

631
00:54:16,962 --> 00:54:19,798
all of us would still be
living like gangsters.

632
00:54:21,299 --> 00:54:22,300
Thanks.

633
00:54:24,594 --> 00:54:25,720
Ms. Lee, open your eyes.

634
00:54:25,804 --> 00:54:28,139
Open your eyes, Ms. Lee.

635
00:54:59,546 --> 00:55:01,214
She needs to be hospitalized
for a few more days.

636
00:55:03,174 --> 00:55:06,428
Things might have gotten bad
if it weren't for you.

637
00:55:13,601 --> 00:55:15,353
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

638
00:55:15,437 --> 00:55:16,271
Congratulations!

639
00:55:20,650 --> 00:55:23,445
Good work, everybody.
This is all thanks to you.

640
00:55:23,528 --> 00:55:24,404
Let's have a drink.

641
00:55:27,615 --> 00:55:28,908
-Cheers.
-Great work!

642
00:55:28,992 --> 00:55:31,202
-Great work!
-Great work!

643
00:55:43,256 --> 00:55:44,382
We're over now.

644
00:55:45,008 --> 00:55:47,260
I don't think
I'll be able to see you again.

645
00:55:55,143 --> 00:55:55,977
Sir.

646
00:55:57,103 --> 00:55:59,731
-Where are you headed?
-I need to go somewhere.

647
00:56:00,482 --> 00:56:01,858
So-ra, that brat.

648
00:56:02,358 --> 00:56:04,569
She can't even
keep track of her own husband?

649
00:56:05,111 --> 00:56:07,655
How useless can she be
to embarrass me in public?

650
00:56:08,281 --> 00:56:10,408
Find where she is, quick.

651
00:56:11,659 --> 00:56:12,494
Yes, sir.

652
00:56:15,038 --> 00:56:16,039
So-ra.

653
00:56:16,122 --> 00:56:19,501
I tried to calm down your father,
but it's not working.

654
00:56:19,584 --> 00:56:20,835
He's on his way to see you.

655
00:56:53,618 --> 00:56:54,911
I'm in front of your house.

656
00:56:56,329 --> 00:56:57,372
I miss you so much.

657
00:56:59,582 --> 00:57:00,708
It's driving me crazy.

658
00:57:01,918 --> 00:57:02,877
I need just a moment.

659
00:57:04,629 --> 00:57:06,256
Let me see you for just a moment.

660
00:57:08,967 --> 00:57:10,385
I can't do that.

661
00:57:11,636 --> 00:57:13,138
Think about Ms. Han.

662
00:57:13,221 --> 00:57:14,222
I know that.

663
00:57:15,640 --> 00:57:18,143
But you're the only one I could think of
on a day like this.

664
00:57:18,226 --> 00:57:19,477
Please, just let me see your face.

665
00:57:21,146 --> 00:57:22,188
I'm begging you.

666
00:57:24,607 --> 00:57:26,025
We're over.

667
00:57:56,806 --> 00:57:57,640
Chairman Kang.

668
00:58:01,811 --> 00:58:03,521
How dare you show up here?

669
00:58:04,105 --> 00:58:06,191
Jin-wook found out about you two.

670
00:58:07,192 --> 00:58:08,568
Don't cause any more problems.

671
00:58:08,651 --> 00:58:10,862
If you don't heed my warning now,

672
00:58:11,446 --> 00:58:13,364
you'll regret it
for the rest of your life.

673
00:58:25,752 --> 00:58:27,212
Please return home, ma'am.

674
00:58:27,295 --> 00:58:28,630
I'll be fine on my own.

675
00:58:29,714 --> 00:58:30,840
Lie down.

676
00:58:31,424 --> 00:58:32,467
I'll be all right.

677
00:58:39,557 --> 00:58:40,934
You seem like a good person.

678
00:58:58,785 --> 00:59:00,995
Do you know
where Chairman Kang's task force team

679
00:59:01,621 --> 00:59:04,082
is holding their celebration party?

680
00:59:48,418 --> 00:59:50,753
Ms. Kim Sun-bin
sent this to your office, sir.

681
01:00:17,739 --> 01:00:20,241
PIAZZOLLA
1968, BUENOS AIRES

682
01:00:45,767 --> 01:00:48,019
It's Piazzolla's bandoneon.

683
01:00:49,103 --> 01:00:52,231
I noticed your scar.

684
01:00:54,233 --> 01:00:56,361
That scar may never fade,

685
01:00:57,195 --> 01:00:58,363
but the heart…

686
01:01:00,156 --> 01:01:02,367
may be healed, little by little.

687
01:01:07,080 --> 01:01:08,623
I hope this bandoneon

688
01:01:09,457 --> 01:01:10,667
can comfort you

689
01:01:11,668 --> 01:01:14,253
just as much as it can comfort

690
01:01:15,463 --> 01:01:17,048
the soul of your late mother.

691
01:02:15,356 --> 01:02:16,399
I missed you.

692
01:02:19,068 --> 01:02:21,195
I can't live without you.

693
01:02:21,988 --> 01:02:23,656
Please don't say that it's over.

694
01:02:25,324 --> 01:02:26,159
Please.

695
01:02:30,580 --> 01:02:31,664
Chairman Kang!

696
01:02:37,462 --> 01:02:38,880
What do you think you're doing?

697
01:02:39,464 --> 01:02:41,048
You think you're entitled?

698
01:02:41,132 --> 01:02:43,509
She's my wife, do you understand?

699
01:02:44,969 --> 01:02:46,137
Honey.

700
01:02:48,181 --> 01:02:50,641
Did I surprise you
by calling you out of the blue?

701
01:02:50,725 --> 01:02:53,352
Not at all. I'm so happy right now.

702
01:02:53,436 --> 01:02:55,813
Let's go look at the view
and have a drink too.

703
01:02:56,564 --> 01:02:57,523
Thanks so much.

704
01:02:58,524 --> 01:02:59,525
Let's go.

705
01:03:04,113 --> 01:03:05,198
Come here.

706
01:03:05,782 --> 01:03:06,991
Calm down, Jin-wook.

707
01:03:07,742 --> 01:03:10,036
How dare you tell me to calm down?

708
01:03:10,119 --> 01:03:11,621
Don't do this, honey.

709
01:03:11,704 --> 01:03:14,415
Why are you holding me back, honey?

710
01:03:14,499 --> 01:03:16,125
You should be stopping him instead!

711
01:03:16,709 --> 01:03:18,002
Jin-wook!

712
01:03:19,545 --> 01:03:20,838
Are you okay?

713
01:03:21,339 --> 01:03:22,423
Don't touch her.

714
01:03:22,507 --> 01:03:24,550
And who are you to tell me that?

715
01:03:24,634 --> 01:03:26,302
She's my wife.

716
01:03:26,385 --> 01:03:27,637
She's mine!

717
01:03:27,720 --> 01:03:31,015
You can't approach her
while you're acting this way.

718
01:03:33,351 --> 01:03:34,602
You're the chairman.

719
01:03:35,520 --> 01:03:37,897
Yet you stole my wife,
and now you're threatening me?

720
01:03:38,773 --> 01:03:40,316
This will be the end of you.

721
01:03:40,399 --> 01:03:42,068
You'll be screwed
once people find out, understand?

722
01:03:42,151 --> 01:03:43,778
You can only yell at me like this

723
01:03:44,529 --> 01:03:46,155
because you're legally her husband.

724
01:03:47,532 --> 01:03:49,617
Then I guess
I'll just take care of it legally.

725
01:03:50,493 --> 01:03:51,327
What?

726
01:03:52,078 --> 01:03:53,830
Are you saying you'll make us divorce?

727
01:03:55,706 --> 01:03:56,999
I'm Kang Yoon-gyeom.

728
01:03:57,583 --> 01:03:59,085
I've always taken everything
I ever wanted.

729
01:04:01,754 --> 01:04:03,631
You're insane.

730
01:04:04,257 --> 01:04:06,175
You're seriously crazy.

731
01:04:06,759 --> 01:04:08,177
You are too, aren't you?

732
01:04:09,595 --> 01:04:12,223
Anyone would go crazy
over a woman like her, after all.

733
01:04:17,436 --> 01:04:19,522
I can't end things with you.

734
01:04:21,899 --> 01:04:23,442
I have a question.

735
01:04:24,986 --> 01:04:26,904
I'm assuming your disappearance back then

736
01:04:28,197 --> 01:04:30,908
was for an intentional purpose.

737
01:04:34,412 --> 01:04:35,371
What were you waiting for?

738
01:04:36,706 --> 01:04:38,124
The critical point.

739
01:04:41,168 --> 01:04:42,879
You mean, when the water boils over?

740
01:04:44,630 --> 01:04:46,591
Water doesn't start boiling suddenly.

741
01:04:48,301 --> 01:04:49,468
Ten degrees.

742
01:04:50,678 --> 01:04:52,471
Twenty degrees and seventy degrees.

743
01:04:54,932 --> 01:04:56,559
Water boils over

744
01:04:56,642 --> 01:04:59,103
when it reaches the critical point
after all its steps.

745
01:05:00,688 --> 01:05:02,523
Then it changes form from gas to liquid,

746
01:05:03,482 --> 01:05:05,526
something entirely different.

747
01:05:16,829 --> 01:05:18,164
Humans are the same.

748
01:05:19,665 --> 01:05:21,292
When we reach the critical point,

749
01:05:22,293 --> 01:05:25,755
we lose our ability to reason
and do things we shouldn’t do.

750
01:05:32,261 --> 01:05:33,429
Drive!

751
01:05:34,263 --> 01:05:35,264
Hurry!

752
01:05:36,140 --> 01:05:39,810
La-el is very close
to making So-ra get a divorce.

753
01:05:40,394 --> 01:05:41,354
Tell Yoon-gyeom

754
01:05:42,146 --> 01:05:44,607
that La-el is Lee Tae-joon's daughter.

755
01:05:45,274 --> 01:05:46,442
Do it as soon as you can.

756
01:05:46,943 --> 01:05:48,778
Doing things we shouldn't do

757
01:05:48,861 --> 01:05:51,113
when we've passed the critical point.

758
01:05:51,989 --> 01:05:53,658
How are you planning to use that?

759
01:05:56,118 --> 01:05:57,662
It'll give me a chance

760
01:05:58,871 --> 01:06:01,332
to change a fate that was God-given.

761
01:06:37,076 --> 01:06:39,996
I won't regret anything,

762
01:06:40,079 --> 01:06:41,664
even if the worst happens to me.

763
01:06:42,456 --> 01:06:44,333
Why did you call me here?

764
01:06:45,751 --> 01:06:46,752
Honey.

765
01:06:48,546 --> 01:06:49,880
You've tried so hard.

766
01:06:49,964 --> 01:06:53,551
I wonder why So-ra hates me so much.

767
01:06:53,634 --> 01:06:54,593
What a psychopath.

768
01:06:55,136 --> 01:06:56,387
I can't just let you off, can I?

769
01:06:57,680 --> 01:06:58,848
It'll be thrilling, for sure.

770
01:06:58,931 --> 01:07:00,099
I'm going to do

771
01:07:00,975 --> 01:07:03,894
my very best to ruin your life.

